        "jsCode": "// Merge the poll response with the carried-forward pipeline data\nconst pollData = $json;\nconst baseData = $('Init D-ID Polling').first().json;\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...baseData,\n    ...pollData\n  }\n}];"
